     Created: 2026-03-19
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Catppuccin Latte theme. Warm pastel
         light palette: cream (#EFF1F5) background with mauve (#8839EF) accent,
         blue (#1E66F5) highlights and muted dark (#4C4F69) text. The elegant
         light counterpart to Catppuccin Mocha.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in CatppuccinLatteTheme.xaml.
         This is a light theme — entry .xaml merges Light/ shared templates (not Dark/).
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Light/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

